        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "need to see what the demand is. \n\n`vim.pack` is intended to be minimal, not an endlessly growing platform. returning low-level data might be fine, that typically does not require a lot of code and unblocks those wanting to build on `vim.pack`.\n\ndo you have a patch you can share here, showing the idea?",
